data.thought: S21|H|S20|Meta-notebook Phenotype D1: 'Notebook Generator'. Input: natural language description of desired notebook behavior. Process: (1) Thoughtbox reasons about structure (cells, deps, flow) (2) Generates .src.md content (3) Validates via container execution (4) Iterates based on errors. Observable: generation reasoning, candidate notebooks, validation results. Output: working notebook from description. Use case: rapid prototyping, teaching, democratizing notebook creation.
